Container class;

    *array is a container class, Its fixed size arrays. 

Template define;
std::array<type, 10> arr;

Access functions;
at -> return value of type
front -> return ptr
back -> return ptr
data -> return ptr

iterators;
begin -> standart iterator
end -> standart iterator
rbegin -> reverse iterator
rend -> reverse iterator

Size / Capasity
empty -> return true or false
size -> return array's size

operators;
std::swap(array1 ,array2) -> swap 2 array
arr->fill(X) -> fill all elements with X

reverse copy;

std::reverse_copy(array1.begin(), array1.end(), 
                      std::ostream_iterator<int>(std::cout, " "));    -> from end to first print data

operators
array[x] -> access x. element
